#: /home/visago/Desktop/olvid/nextcloud/workspace/server/apps-extra/olvid/src/views/ProfileView.vue:139
msgid ""
"Warning: this action is not reversible. Your Olvid identity will be blocked "
"for every other contact in this directory. They will no longer be able to "
"reach you through this identity, and it can never be re-registered. You will "
"need to create a new Olvid profile and re-enroll."
